          "subtitle": "Core lessons for smarter AI decisions",
          "slidecontent": "• AI predictions can and do fail, so always have a backup plan ready\n• Errors in forecasting can ripple quickly through your entire supply chain\n• Monitor outputs regularly\n• Understanding why a prediction failed matters as much as fixing the immediate problem\n• Small data quality issues often cause the biggest operational disruptions\n• Start by reviewing one process where AI supports decisions and test its accuracy this week"
